quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  74,48,Nafataa…ìe tefoore tefoo…ìe
  74,49,Hol ko wa…ói …ìe sirku…ìe na …óuurno Quraana
  74,50,Ho…ìe mba*i e bam…ói laawatoo…ói na ndoga
  74,51,Dok…ói mbaroodi
  74,52,Gooto e mum en fof na faaala totteede …óeri caraa…ói
  74,53,Alah woni ko…ìe kulaani laakara
  74,54,Alah …óuum ko ciftanirgol
  74,55,Ko kala faalaa…óo waactaroo mbo o waaccaroo mbo
  74,56,"…ìe mbaactaaka si wonah Alla na haaja, ko Kanko woni kaandu…óo e huleede ko Kanko woni kaandu…óo e yaafaade"
  75,1,Mbe…óa woondira √±ande ndarnga
  75,2,Mbe…óa woondira fittaandu felooru
  75,3,Mbela aade sikkat Min ndenndintah ∆¥i*e makko
  75,4,Oho kay mbe…óa Min kattani fotndude gulle pe…óeeli makko
  75,5,Kono aade yi…ói konde o wonata saay yeeso ka yeeso makko
  75,6,"Hi…ìe lamndoo : \"Ko honnde woni √ëalaande njo…ìdi kuu…óe"
  75,7,Si yitere majii
  75,8,Lewru nanngaa
  75,9,Naange e lewru ndenndina
  75,10,Ndeen aade wi*a ho…óo dogirde woni
  75,11,Alah dogdu alah e oon √±alngu
  75,12,Koto joom ma √±ande heen nwoni ruttorde
  75,13,Aade na habre √±ande heen ko ardini e golle e ko o leelni
  75,14,Ko woni ko aade na seedii e fittaandu makko
  75,15,Hay si o addii ngantuuji makko
  75,16,Woto dillin heen …óemngal Ma haa njaawna…óa e hembo
  75,17,Ko Minen woodani renndinde mbo e jannginde mbo Ma
  75,18,Si Min njanngii mbo rew e jande makko
  75,19,Refti ko e Amen fawi firde mbo
